The license permits a single installation of Sitecore Software per Server (as Server is defined in the Agreement). The license permits one (1) Sitecore System (as that term is defined in the Agreement).

The license allows up to 10 Sitecore Users (Concurrent).

Licensee may use the Sitecore Software exclusively for the management of Licensee’s own current and future public-facing web properties (the “Permitted Usage”).
